1
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:33,320
[Echo of Her Voice]

2
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,250
[Episode 13]

3
00:02:18,830 --> 00:02:19,590
Xiaoqi.

4
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:22,230
Xiaoqi.

5
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:27,340
Young Lord, what’s wrong?

6
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:28,540
Is there an assassin?

7
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,350
Go ask her

8
00:02:31,510 --> 00:02:32,880
is she going to sleep or not?

9
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:35,610
She's been disturbing me all night. I can't rest.

10
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:40,720
Why are you still standing there?

11
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,430
Go quickly!

12
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:47,930
Ms. Su,

13
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:50,510
the Young Lord asks if you're going to sleep.

14
00:02:50,510 --> 00:02:51,660
Tell him that

15
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:54,190
he's the one tossing and turning.

16
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,850
He's making so much noise I can't sleep.

17
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:57,910
Tell him to stop being unerasonable.

18
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,810
She says you're being unreasonable.

19
00:03:06,810 --> 00:03:08,260
I'm unreasonable?

20
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:11,990
I sent you to Symphony Workshop

21
00:03:11,990 --> 00:03:13,430
to be a musician,

22
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:15,110
not to reminisce with Jin Shangyu,

23
00:03:15,110 --> 00:03:15,950
causing controversy

24
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:18,410
and affecting the reputation of my mansion.

25
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:19,110
Go.

26
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,190
The Young Lord said—

27
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:26,090
He shouldn't say anything.

28
00:03:26,090 --> 00:03:27,400
As the Young Lord,

29
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:30,390
he's actually joining those people in making groundless accusations.

30
00:03:30,390 --> 00:03:32,080
Shangyu and I are buddies

31
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,990
who grew up together since childhood.

32
00:03:33,990 --> 00:03:35,230
Certain people don't believe me

33
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:37,050
and are even spreading rumors over there.

34
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:37,610
Go.

35
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,000
I'm spreading rumors?

36
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:49,030
To make a groundless accusation, there must be something to accuse.

37
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:49,750
Without that,

38
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:52,230
others can't make accusations even if they want.

39
00:03:52,230 --> 00:03:52,870
Moreover,

40
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,400
you went to practice with Jin Shangyu

41
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,330
and you two were all touchy-feely.

42
00:03:57,690 --> 00:03:59,190
If that's not grounds for accusations, what is it?

43
00:03:59,190 --> 00:03:59,710
Go.

44
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,190
You are

45
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:05,750
seriously so petty.

46
00:04:12,950 --> 00:04:14,550
What is she doing over there?

47
00:04:15,950 --> 00:04:16,630
She said...

48
00:04:16,650 --> 00:04:17,670
Said what?

49
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,590
You're seriously so petty.

50
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,070
You dare to insult me?

51
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:31,510
I didn't insult you.

52
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,790
Then who insulted me?

53
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:35,270
I insulted you.

54
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,000
You two can argue by yourselves.

55
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:10,110
[Young Lord's Mansion]

56
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,460
Oh, right.

57
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:27,580
Doesn't he have a sweetheart?

58
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:30,720
I'll show her portrait to my sister.

59
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:33,390
Let her see this little devil's true colors.

60
00:05:59,150 --> 00:06:00,470
It's her.

61
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:03,540
The little devil even said I know her.

62
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:07,150
She does look familiar.

63
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:14,800
This—

64
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:22,110
This is too familiar.

65
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:25,860
It can't be me, can it?

66
00:06:26,990 --> 00:06:32,010
The little devil actually likes me?

67
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:35,540
It can't be.

68
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,560
This is definitely a trap.

69
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:54,500
[Symphony Workshop]

70
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:58,750
Why are you following me?

71
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,500
I'm not following you.

72
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,550
I came to Symphony Workshop

73
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:04,110
to fulfill my supervisory duty.

74
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:05,370
What are you thinking?

75
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,470
It's so pretty.

76
00:07:25,470 --> 00:07:26,710
I think yours is pretty.

77
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:27,990
Look, it's purple.

78
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,030
Why are they dressed the same as you?

79
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:38,350
What's going on here?

80
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:40,130
Young Lord.

81
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:42,160
Sister.

82
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:45,200
Ruoshan, no need for formalities.

83
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:46,630
Sister.

84
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,260
Did you come specially to pick me up?

85
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:49,990
I do have something to tell you.

86
00:07:50,990 --> 00:07:52,150
Is it convenient?

87
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:53,950
Of course.

88
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:54,600
Let's go.

89
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:03,430
Did you see how those people were dressed?

90
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:08,430
Go ahead.

91
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:11,550
Did you see

92
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:13,490
how those people were all wearing

93
00:08:13,710 --> 00:08:15,350
jiegu drum headpieces and bracelets?

94
00:08:15,350 --> 00:08:16,550
I just saw it.

95
00:08:16,550 --> 00:08:17,480
I was going to ask you about it.

96
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,630
What's going on?

97
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:21,270
You're still trying to play dumb?

98
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:22,830
Yesterday, Master Jin

99
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:24,430
publicly described what kind of girl

100
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,430
he likes.

101
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:28,020
These girls heard what he said.

102
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:30,250
That's why they dressed up like this.

103
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:34,230
So, Mr. Jin is the one you have feelings for.

104
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,900
How is that possible?

105
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:38,640
Then tell me,

106
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:40,750
who is it that you have feelings for?

107
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:41,590
I...

108
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:43,830
It's...

109
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:50,940
It's...

110
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,110
Alright.

111
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:54,070
You won't even tell your sister the truth.

112
00:08:54,070 --> 00:08:55,110
Yesterday, Mr. Jin

113
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,720
gave such obvious hints in public,

114
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,320
yet you still want to deny it.

115
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:00,380
Ruoshan,

116
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:04,190
maybe Shangyu was just saying that casually,

117
00:09:04,350 --> 00:09:05,120
while those people took it seriously.

118
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,180
Alright, alright.

119
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:07,630
I know you're shy.

120
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,710
But even if you don't like him,

121
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:13,270
how do you know Mr. Jin doesn't like you?

122
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:18,530
I've said all I need to say.

123
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:20,800
You should think about it carefully.

124
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:22,990
By the way,

125
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:25,820
do you want to participate in the musician audition

126
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:27,010
for the ceremony?

127
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:29,110
Of course I want to participate.

128
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:32,640
Although I might not be able to beat you,

129
00:09:32,870 --> 00:09:34,190
even if I lose,

130
00:09:34,190 --> 00:09:36,850
it's still a rare opportunity for me to improve.

131
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:38,030
Good.

132
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:40,830
I also look forward to competing with you on the same stage.

133
00:09:40,830 --> 00:09:42,630
This is a rare opportunity.

134
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:44,590
The Symphony Workshop is full of talented people.

135
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:45,600
Don't slack off.

136
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:46,430
Don't worry.

137
00:09:46,430 --> 00:09:47,830
I won't let you down.

138
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,740
I'm going to practice now.

139
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,070
Go ahead.

140
00:09:56,070 --> 00:09:57,200
I'm off to practice.

141
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:06,450
Young Lord,

142
00:10:07,070 --> 00:10:08,800
I just asked Fei specifically.

143
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,800
Fei...

144
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:14,670
indeed has feelings for Master Jin.

145
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:18,070
Although this girl doesn't truly understand it,

146
00:10:18,070 --> 00:10:19,190
her feelings

147
00:10:19,310 --> 00:10:20,620
can't be hidden.

148
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:27,840
Ruoshan, thank you.

149
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:32,110
I'll head off now.

150
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:44,800
Now that the seed of suspicion has been planted,

151
00:10:45,090 --> 00:10:47,750
I'll just wait for it to take root and bear fruit.

152
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:50,990
Only by making the Young Lord completely give up on Fei

153
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:53,750
will I have a chance to get him back in my grasp.

154
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,700
This is so annoying.

155
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,630
They locked me up for so long.

156
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:04,350
I wonder if my Jin misses me.

157
00:11:15,130 --> 00:11:16,970
Why are they copying Su Ruofei?

158
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:23,880
What are they...

159
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:26,170
What's going on with them?

160
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:30,160
Have you all gone crazy?

161
00:11:31,610 --> 00:11:33,540
I'm not too sure about the details.

162
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:35,500
I heard it's because yesterday, Master Jin

163
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:38,100
publicly described what kind of girl he likes.

164
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:53,430
Shangyu likes me?

165
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,270
How is that possible?

166
00:11:55,330 --> 00:11:57,190
Ruoshan must be overthinking it.

167
00:11:58,030 --> 00:12:00,950
But those musicians' outfits...

168
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:04,050
In terms of looks and ability,

169
00:12:04,310 --> 00:12:06,040
where exactly did I fall short?

170
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:18,930
Huang Ying.

171
00:12:18,950 --> 00:12:19,790
You're back.

172
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:20,920
How did it go?

173
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:21,870
It's fine now.

174
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:24,220
The timbre of your drum is quite good.

175
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,100
May I try it?

176
00:12:28,310 --> 00:12:30,070
This is my favorite drum.

177
00:12:30,830 --> 00:12:32,630
The timbre is indeed quite good.

178
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:37,810
Huang Ying!

179
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:39,510
You...

180
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:42,700
Why did you break my drum?

181
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,030
I'm sorry.

182
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,430
Your drum is not sturdy enough.

183
00:12:45,430 --> 00:12:46,090
Huang Ying.

184
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:47,770
You went too far.

185
00:12:47,770 --> 00:12:49,240
Why are you so angry?

186
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:50,550
It's not your drum.

187
00:12:50,990 --> 00:12:52,670
Since I broke it, I'll just pay her for it, alright?

188
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:53,400
How dare you!

189
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,230
Now that you're in the Symphony Workshop,

190
00:12:55,230 --> 00:12:56,790
you must follow the rules here.

191
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,870
You openly damaged a fellow musician's instrument.

192
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,160
This will be recorded as a major demerit.

193
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,460
If there's a next time,

194
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:03,350
you'll be stripped of your musician status

195
00:13:03,350 --> 00:13:05,680
and expelled from the Symphony Workshop.

196
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,350
Fine.

197
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:09,710
Now I understand.

198
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:12,670
You two are both on her side, aren't you?

199
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,030
Alright.

200
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:16,150
No need to wait for next time.

201
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,110
I'll do it right now.

202
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:17,770
Huang Ying!

203
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,480
Haven't you caused enough trouble?

204
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:22,660
Ruofei.

205
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:24,030
I'm sorry.

206
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:25,350
Come with me.

207
00:13:26,010 --> 00:13:26,670
Let's go.

208
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:34,390
You're hurting me.

209
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,950
I was too lenient with you before, was I?

210
00:13:37,950 --> 00:13:39,070
Do you need to be taught a lesson

211
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:39,790
to behave properly?

212
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,600
What lesson are you going to teach me?

213
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,480
Then hit me!

214
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,190
Hit me.

215
00:13:44,310 --> 00:13:44,660
Hit me!

216
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:44,880
Stop it!

217
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:45,390
[Breeze Pavilion]
Stop it!

218
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:47,800
[Breeze Pavilion]

219
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:48,920
Why did you break Su Ruofei's drum?
[Breeze Pavilion]

220
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,030
Why did you break Su Ruofei's drum?

221
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,270
Because you like her!

222
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,390
Don't think I don't know that those people

223
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,270
dressed up like that

224
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,580
all because of Su Ruofei!

225
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,210
Yes.

226
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:57,980
I do like her.

227
00:13:58,290 --> 00:13:59,910
Now you know there's no possibility between us.

228
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:00,970
Why do you like her?

229
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:02,550
Why do I like her?

230
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:04,330
Does liking someone need a reason?

231
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:05,190
What about her?

232
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,050
Does she like you?

233
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:15,980
Does she know you like her?

234
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,470
You haven't told her?

235
00:14:20,850 --> 00:14:22,730
You don't even dare to tell her.

236
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:24,940
And you still say you like her?

237
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:26,380
Who says I don't dare?

238
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:27,310
I don't believe you dare.

239
00:14:27,310 --> 00:14:28,230
Go tell her now.

240
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,030
Fine, I'll go.

241
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:47,100
What's wrong? Don't want to go anymore?

242
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:49,870
I know what you're afraid of.

243
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:53,030
You're afraid she doesn't like you.

244
00:14:53,470 --> 00:14:55,320
You're afraid that if you tell her,

245
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,110
the relationship between you two

246
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:58,550
will become even more distant than it is now.

247
00:14:58,550 --> 00:15:00,750
So, you don't actually like Su Ruofei.

248
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:02,120
What gives you the right to say that?

249
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:04,650
Do you know how many times you've rejected me?

250
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,810
I'm not afraid of being rejected by you at all.

251
00:15:06,810 --> 00:15:07,510
I'm only afraid

252
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:09,170
that you don't know I like you.

253
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:10,720
I'm not afraid that you don't like me either.

254
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,830
I'm only afraid of losing you,

255
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:12,670
you know?

256
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:15,180
So, you don't actually like Su Ruofei.

257
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:23,460
You're right.

258
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:25,520
I shouldn't be afraid.

259
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:29,190
So what if she rejects me?

260
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:33,600
What I should really be afraid of

261
00:15:34,950 --> 00:15:37,280
is that I've liked her for so many years...

262
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:39,790
Yet she never knew.

263
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:16,960
Ruofei.

264
00:16:18,430 --> 00:16:19,430
I'm truly sorry.

265
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:23,120
Huang Ying did this because of me.

266
00:16:23,270 --> 00:16:24,620
Don't say sorry.

267
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,090
This isn't your fault.

268
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:27,420
How about this?

269
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:29,950
I'll try my best to repair this drum.

270
00:16:29,970 --> 00:16:30,910
If I can't fix it,

271
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:32,680
I'll buy you a new one, okay?

272
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:36,090
This has nothing to do with you.

273
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:37,430
Don't feel guilty.

274
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:44,390
Actually, it's not guilt.

275
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:47,990
Because...

276
00:16:50,070 --> 00:16:51,730
Your business is my business.

277
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,840
I can't run away anymore.

278
00:16:59,470 --> 00:17:00,140
Today,

279
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:04,860
I must say everything I want to say.

280
00:17:06,290 --> 00:17:07,210
Ruofei.

281
00:17:09,180 --> 00:17:10,320
They're not wrong.

282
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,650
Huang Ying is not wrong either.

283
00:17:13,870 --> 00:17:15,070
I do like you.

284
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,760
Shangyu,

285
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:26,270
stop joking with me.

