00:41:50,820 --> 00:41:53,270
He must be going through his own tribulation.

815
00:41:53,270 --> 00:41:55,080
Alright, let's not talk about him.

816
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:56,270
When do we start?

817
00:41:59,110 --> 00:41:59,670
Okay.

818
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:02,750
Since we've chosen to work together,

819
00:42:02,910 --> 00:42:05,240
there are some things I need to make clear.

820
00:42:05,700 --> 00:42:08,040
Regardless of my relationship with the Young Lord,

821
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:08,960
we must

822
00:42:09,030 --> 00:42:10,430
rely on our own abilities this time

823
00:42:10,430 --> 00:42:11,560
to win the audition.

824
00:42:12,090 --> 00:42:14,750
I know there will be a lot of

825
00:42:14,790 --> 00:42:16,490
gossip about me in the future,

826
00:42:16,730 --> 00:42:19,000
but I can use my music

827
00:42:19,030 --> 00:42:20,490
to disprove those rumors.

828
00:42:20,930 --> 00:42:22,360
I need your help too.

829
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:24,560
Let's work together to make the Qinghe Group

830
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:26,380
the best group in the Symphony Workshop.

831
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,440
-Come on!
-Come on!

832
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:34,340
Alright, let's begin.

833
00:42:36,630 --> 00:42:37,510
Who is it?

834
00:42:42,370 --> 00:42:43,890
Ruoshan, why are you here?

835
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:46,390
I have something to tell you.

836
00:42:46,390 --> 00:42:47,270
Do you have a moment?

837
00:42:47,270 --> 00:42:48,030
Sure.

838
00:42:49,710 --> 00:42:51,230
You all familiarize yourselves with the music first.

839
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:52,270
I'll be back soon.

840
00:42:52,580 --> 00:42:53,180
Let's go.

841
00:43:05,750 --> 00:43:06,410
Have a seat.

842
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:13,170
Ruoshan,

843
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:15,440
what's so mysterious

844
00:43:15,470 --> 00:43:16,970
that you had to bring me here?

845
00:43:16,970 --> 00:43:18,410
Tell me the truth.

846
00:43:18,830 --> 00:43:21,800
What exactly is your relationship with the Young Lord?

847
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:23,460
Young Lord and I?

848
00:43:27,410 --> 00:43:29,610
I wasn't sure before,

849
00:43:31,730 --> 00:43:33,450
but now I believe

850
00:43:33,910 --> 00:43:35,350
Young Lord and I

851
00:43:36,630 --> 00:43:38,690
have mutual feelings for each other.

852
00:43:45,180 --> 00:43:47,870
As sisters, I never thought

853
00:43:48,470 --> 00:43:51,000
that we would fall for the same person one day.

854
00:43:52,030 --> 00:43:53,440
The same person?

855
00:43:57,030 --> 00:43:57,860
Ruoshan,

856
00:43:58,870 --> 00:44:00,350
do you also...

857
00:44:00,670 --> 00:44:01,390
Fei,

858
00:44:01,740 --> 00:44:03,680
I have sincere feelings for Young Lord.

859
00:44:03,680 --> 00:44:05,940
Can you please let him be with me instead?

860
00:44:06,450 --> 00:44:07,670
-Ruoshan...
-Fei,

861
00:44:07,790 --> 00:44:09,050
I've always let you have your way in everything,

862
00:44:09,050 --> 00:44:10,210
always giving in to you.

863
00:44:10,210 --> 00:44:12,080
Can you give in to me just this once?

864
00:44:12,080 --> 00:44:13,480
Let Young Lord be with me.

865
00:44:14,090 --> 00:44:14,920
-Give him to me.
-Ruoshan.

866
00:44:14,920 --> 00:44:15,810
Ruoshan.

867
00:44:17,370 --> 00:44:18,380
I know

868
00:44:18,390 --> 00:44:20,650
you've always been good to me since we were little.

869
00:44:20,650 --> 00:44:22,200
We're very close,

870
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:24,290
even closer than with our parents.

871
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:26,030
Whatever you want,

872
00:44:26,050 --> 00:44:26,870
as long as I have it,

873
00:44:26,870 --> 00:44:28,120
I'll give it to you.

874
00:44:29,640 --> 00:44:32,850
But Yun Mu is a person.

875
00:44:33,350 --> 00:44:35,230
I have no right to decide

876
00:44:35,310 --> 00:44:36,590
what he should choose.

877
00:44:37,230 --> 00:44:40,690
Yun Mu and I have mutual feelings for each other.

878
00:44:42,270 --> 00:44:44,010
I can give you anything,

879
00:44:44,040 --> 00:44:46,710
but feelings are the one thing I'm unable to give

880
00:44:47,770 --> 00:44:48,700
and can't give.

881
00:44:54,810 --> 00:44:55,630
Ruoshan.

882
00:44:57,430 --> 00:44:58,710
There's another way.

883
00:44:58,790 --> 00:44:59,280
Fei,

884
00:44:59,310 --> 00:45:00,510
there's another way.

885
00:45:00,530 --> 00:45:01,930
We're already sisters.

886
00:45:02,090 --> 00:45:04,160
We can both marry him, right?

887
00:45:04,330 --> 00:45:05,460
After marrying him,

888
00:45:05,480 --> 00:45:06,830
we'll still be sisters.

889
00:45:06,880 --> 00:45:08,190
Let's marry him together, okay?

890
00:45:08,190 --> 00:45:08,950
Ruoshan!

891
00:45:13,980 --> 00:45:14,900
I'm sorry.

892
00:45:26,760 --> 00:45:28,160
You really won't give in?

893
00:45:30,200 --> 00:45:31,380
I can't give in.

894
00:45:32,520 --> 00:45:33,720
I don't have the right

895
00:45:33,750 --> 00:45:35,550
to make this decision for Yun Mu.

896
00:45:37,170 --> 00:45:37,970
I understand.

897
00:45:38,660 --> 00:45:39,200
You can leave now.

898
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:39,670
Ruoshan.

899
00:45:39,670 --> 00:45:40,350
Get out!

900
00:45:43,900 --> 00:45:45,610
Then let's talk again

901
00:45:46,100 --> 00:45:47,500
when you've calmed down.

902
00:45:59,740 --> 00:46:00,510
Fei,

903
00:46:01,730 --> 00:46:03,150
I gave you a chance.

904
00:46:04,870 --> 00:46:06,550
You're the one who refused.

905
00:46:08,710 --> 00:46:10,670
Don't blame me for being heartless then.
